  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t连词代词what, who, which, whose等引导的主语从句。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t这些连接代词作用相当于代词，在从句中担当主语、宾语、表语、定语等。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;What we need is more time.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;Who was responsible for the accident is not yet clear.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;Whose book it is not important.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;Which school you want to go matters much.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t连接副词when, where, why, how引导的主语从句。</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;这些连接副词相当于副词，在从句中充当状语。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;Why he did this is not known.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp;When he will come is still unknown.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; It is not known why he did this.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; How he succeeded is unknown to us.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Where we should hold the meeting needs to be discussed.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t注意 wh-引导的主语从句也常用it作形式主语。</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">也可用whatever,whoever,whomever,whenever,wherever等词引导主语从句，表示&ldquo;无论什么&rdquo;、&ldquo;无论谁&rdquo;、&ldquo;无论何时&rdquo;、&ldquo;无论在（到）哪里&rdquo;等。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Whoever told you to give up smoking was quite right.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Whatever he gave you should be handed in.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Whoever told you that was lying.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; Whoever comes is welcome.</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772476/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p772476\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: